# martinMap

- _martinMap(a, b, c)_

A function by Barry Martin.

Martin map, _a=0.4,b=1,c=0_:

~~~spl svg=A
martinMap(0.4, 1, 0)
.nestList([0 0], 99)
.scatterPlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/martinMap-A.svg)

Martin map, _a=-2,b=0.33,c=0.01_:

~~~spl svg=B
martinMap(-2, -0.33, 0.01)
.nestList([0 0], 99)
.scatterPlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/martinMap-B.svg)

Martin map, _a=6,b=-1,c=3_:

~~~spl svg=C
martinMap(6, -1, 3)
.nestList([0 0], 99)
.scatterPlot
~~~

![](Help/Image/martinMap-C.svg)

